"""
╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
║          BACKEND 2 — CHAT COMPONENT (Discord-Style)                 ║
║  Player ↔ Player  |  Player ↔ AI Agent  |  Strategy Planning Room  ║
╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

Features:
  - Multi-channel chat (General, Team ALPHA, Team OMEGA, Strategy Room)
  - Direct messages between players
  - AI agent auto-responses based on their element personality
  - Strategy commands parsed by AI (/strategy, /regroup, /attack, /defend)
